[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":371},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F":347,"related:\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F":356},"\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F19\u002Fvscode-paste-image-upload-to-imgur\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":106,"date":333,"description":18,"extension":334,"lang":335,"meta":336,"navigation":337,"path":338,"readingMinutes":339,"seo":340,"standalone":341,"stem":342,"tags":343,"tldr":344,"updated":344,"url":345,"__hash__":346},"content\u002FVSCode\u002FVSCode-上直接黏貼上傳圖片到-Imgur.md","VSCode 上直接黏貼上傳圖片到 Imgur","2164825737",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":327},"minimark",[11,15,19,26,29,39,43,58,61,71,76,79,87,92,95,100,103,107,116,121,124,129,132,188,191,196,199,204,207,212,215,220,223,228,231,234,237,242,245,256,261,264,269,272,277,280,285,291,294,316,323],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"由於自己在撰寫文章已經轉至使用 VSCode，但是圖片空間說實在每次都要透過 Imgur 網站上傳再複製網址貼到 md 內實在很不方便，這邊剛好找到一個套件覺得超強的，範例就像這樣",[16,20,21],{},[22,23],"img",{"alt":24,"src":25},"圖片","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjPm7V6t.gif",[16,27,28],{},"所以這邊紀錄一下該如何安裝及使用",[30,31,32],"blockquote",{},[16,33,34,38],{},[35,36,37],"strong",{},"Note","\n本系列是針對 Imgur 來做介紹，但是 Imgur 在 2025 年 05 月 16 日之後限制台灣 IP 使用者無法上傳圖片，因此如果你是台灣使用者的話，可能會無法使用 Imgur 上傳圖片，這邊建議可以改用其他圖片上傳服務。",[12,40,42],{"id":41},"imgur","Imgur",[16,44,45,46,52,53],{},"首先先開啟 ",[47,48,42],"a",{"href":49,"rel":50},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002F",[51],"nofollow"," 並註冊登入帳號，然後點這個網址來申請 ",[47,54,57],{"href":55,"rel":56},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[51],"Imgur API",[16,59,60],{},"然後填寫圖片紅框欄位。",[62,63,64,68],"ul",{},[65,66,67],"li",{},"Application name：隨便想，最好自己可以認得",[65,69,70],{},"Authorization type：OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL",[16,72,73],{},[22,74],{"alt":24,"src":75},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FbaiboMe.png",[16,77,78],{},"送出之後就會得到兩個東西，請務必複製留下來。",[62,80,81,84],{},[65,82,83],{},"Client ID",[65,85,86],{},"Client secret",[16,88,89],{},[22,90],{"alt":24,"src":91},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJDbWQvj.png",[16,93,94],{},"如果不小心遺失了就從這裡看，但 Client secret 就必須重新生成。",[16,96,97],{},[22,98],{"alt":24,"src":99},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FS2YXgWJ.png",[16,101,102],{},"※注意網頁先不要關，稍後還會用到。",[12,104,106],{"id":105},"vscode","VSCode",[16,108,109,110,115],{},"接下來要安裝插件，到擴充去搜尋 ",[47,111,114],{"href":112,"rel":113},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=MaxfieldWalker.vscode-imgur",[51],"vscode-imgur","，然後安裝插件。",[16,117,118],{},[22,119],{"alt":24,"src":120},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FDPrgqT0.png",[16,122,123],{},"接下來開啟 VSCode 設定檔，一般來講是 Ctrl + , (Window)或者 設定 > 然後找有 settings.json 的都可以。",[16,125,126],{},[22,127],{"alt":24,"src":128},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FkQuW99p.png",[16,130,131],{},"打開後將下面程式碼貼進去",[133,134,139],"pre",{"className":135,"code":136,"language":137,"meta":138,"style":138},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"vscode-imgur.client_id\": \"剛剛 imgur 的 client_id\",\n\"vscode-imgur.client_secret\": \"剛剛 imgur 的 client_secret\",\n\"vscode-imgur.preferUserUpload\": true,\n","json","",[140,141,142,161,174],"code",{"__ignoreMap":138},[143,144,147,151,155,158],"span",{"class":145,"line":146},"line",1,[143,148,150],{"class":149},"sTRMh","\"vscode-imgur.client_id\"",[143,152,154],{"class":153},"sMAXC",": ",[143,156,157],{"class":149},"\"剛剛 imgur 的 client_id\"",[143,159,160],{"class":153},",\n",[143,162,164,167,169,172],{"class":145,"line":163},2,[143,165,166],{"class":149},"\"vscode-imgur.client_secret\"",[143,168,154],{"class":153},[143,170,171],{"class":149},"\"剛剛 imgur 的 client_secret\"",[143,173,160],{"class":153},[143,175,177,180,182,186],{"class":145,"line":176},3,[143,178,179],{"class":149},"\"vscode-imgur.preferUserUpload\"",[143,181,154],{"class":153},[143,183,185],{"class":184},"sCcAr","true",[143,187,160],{"class":153},[16,189,190],{},"接下來去隨便找一個圖片點右鍵複製圖片",[16,192,193],{},[22,194],{"alt":24,"src":195},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fin5Seuu.png",[16,197,198],{},"然後再 VSCode 的 md 中按下 CTRL + ALT + V，接下來會卡住然後跳出這個視窗",[16,200,201],{},[22,202],{"alt":24,"src":203},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F6RdhBy0.png",[16,205,206],{},"這時候切回去  畫面，它會跟你說有人 vscode-imgur 要使用來上傳圖片，所以你要按允許。",[16,208,209],{},[22,210],{"alt":24,"src":211},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FtPJjSUI.png",[16,213,214],{},"接下來畫面會出現一組 PIN，複製下這組 PIN",[16,216,217],{},[22,218],{"alt":24,"src":219},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FzZy5t5T.png",[16,221,222],{},"將這組 PIN 貼近這裡",[16,224,225],{},[22,226],{"alt":24,"src":227},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJau7SQ6.png",[16,229,230],{},"這樣圖片就可以上傳啦~~",[12,232,233],{"id":233},"相簿分類",[16,235,236],{},"如果希望上傳的圖片可以分類，請先進入 Imgur 開啟相簿",[16,238,239],{},[22,240],{"alt":24,"src":241},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F04iAW7S.png",[16,243,244],{},"依照欄位填寫即可，下方選項看個人，我是使用 public",[62,246,247,250,253],{},[65,248,249],{},"public 公開",[65,251,252],{},"Hidden 隱藏",[65,254,255],{},"Secret 秘密(上鎖?",[16,257,258],{},[22,259],{"alt":24,"src":260},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FtwZFX0a.png",[16,262,263],{},"開啟之後我建議先丟一張圖片上傳，上傳完再點上方 gallery profile",[16,265,266],{},[22,267],{"alt":24,"src":268},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FguezJvh.png",[16,270,271],{},"然後再點 Albums",[16,273,274],{},[22,275],{"alt":24,"src":276},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjZ6ERtG.png",[16,278,279],{},"如果你剛剛有先上傳一張圖片的話，你就可以看到第一張圖片，點進去。",[16,281,282],{},[22,283],{"alt":24,"src":284},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FP3mPkGf.png",[16,286,287,288],{},"點進去後取得網址列最後的相簿代碼，這邊範例是 d7B2zub (a\u002F之後)，記住這個代碼\n",[22,289],{"alt":24,"src":290},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F8DQzjCk.png",[16,292,293],{},"回到 VSCode 打開 settings.json 將這行貼上",[133,295,297],{"className":135,"code":296,"language":137,"meta":138,"style":138},"\"vscode-imgur.album_id\": \"相簿代碼\", \u002F\u002F 我的範例就是 d7B2zub\n",[140,298,299],{"__ignoreMap":138},[143,300,301,304,306,309,312],{"class":145,"line":146},[143,302,303],{"class":149},"\"vscode-imgur.album_id\"",[143,305,154],{"class":153},[143,307,308],{"class":149},"\"相簿代碼\"",[143,310,311],{"class":153},", ",[143,313,315],{"class":314},"sQrFR","\u002F\u002F 我的範例就是 d7B2zub\n",[16,317,318,319],{},"這樣就大功告成啦",[320,321,322],"del",{},"可以嘗試在 VSCode 直接黏貼圖片吧",[324,325,326],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}",{"title":138,"searchDepth":163,"depth":163,"links":328},[329,330,331,332],{"id":14,"depth":163,"text":14},{"id":41,"depth":163,"text":42},{"id":105,"depth":163,"text":106},{"id":233,"depth":163,"text":233},"2019-05-19 20:15:56","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fvscode\u002Fvscode-imgur","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"VSCode\u002FVSCode-上直接黏貼上傳圖片到-Imgur",[106,42],null,"\u002Fvscode\u002F20190519\u002F2164825737\u002F","E5j68Bx0ayYvXhkkUSlpPl9t_JT5cLGCHrRw4F7IggQ",{"newer":348,"older":352},{"url":349,"title":350,"date":351},"\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190519\u002F3792031969\u002F","[JS奇怪的世界]No.33 觀念小叮嚀:語法解析器","2019-05-19 21:10:00",{"url":353,"title":354,"date":355},"\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190519\u002F3614278777\u002F","[